# If you prefer the allow list template instead of the deny list, see community template:
# https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/community/Golang/Go.AllowList.gitignore
#
# Binaries for programs and plugins
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Test binary, built with `go test -c`
*.test

# Code coverage profiles and other test artifacts
*.out
coverage.*
*.coverprofile
profile.cov

# Dependency directories — resolved via go.mod/go.sum, not committed
vendor/

# Go workspace file
go.work
go.work.sum

# env file
.env

# Editor/IDE
# .idea/
# .vscode/

# Streamweave article/cover assets (not part of the codebase)
doc/streamweave-article.html
doc/streamweave-cover-render.html
doc/streamweave-cover.html
doc/streamweave-cover.png
doc/streamweave-linkedin-article.md
